high_descs: Turn left and walk to the small table in the corner of the kitchen
Pick up the butter knife on the table
Turn around and walk to the kitchen table
Slice the bread on the kitchen table
Turn around and go back to the small table in the corner of the kitchen
Place knife down on top of the table next to the salt
Turn around and walk to the kitchen table
Pick up a slice of bread on the table
Turn around and walk towards the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and place the bread inside and close, chill then open and remove
Turn to the left and walk to the small table in the corner of the kitchen
Place the bread on the table
Go to the small black table in front of you and to your left.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn around and go to the white table.
Slice the loaf of bread.
Return to the black table.
Put the knife down.
Return to the white table.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Chill the bread in the fridge.
Turn left and go to the black table.
Put the bread on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of chilled bread on the black table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the table, then turn right.
Pick up the knife in front of the cabbage.
Turn around and carry the knife to the table with the loaves of bread.
Slice the left half of the front loaf of bread.
Turn around and carry the knife across the room.
Set the knife on top of the right salt shaker.
Turn around and walk back across the room to the sliced loaf of bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the middle of the loaf.
Turn around and carry the slice of bread across the room.
Put the slice of bread in the refrigerator, close the refrigerator, then open it and take it back out again.
Turn left and carry the slice of bread across the room.
St the slice of bread down next to the knife and between the middle salt shaker and the right salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Set down a refrigerated slice of bread next to some items on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the white table by the stove, then turn to your right and go to the small, black shelf beside the kitchen cabinets.
Pick up the knife located in front of the head of lettuce closest to you.
Turn around and walk to the small white table with a wooden chair on the left side of it.
Cut the loaf of bread close to the edge into slices.
Turn around and go back to the small, black shelf beside the kitchen cabinets.
Place the knife back on the table by the salt shaker closest to the counter top.
Turn around and go back to the white table where you sliced the bread.
Pick up the the middle slice of bread.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator with the slice of bread.
Place the slice of bread on the top shelf of the refrigerator, leave it in there for a moment, then remove the slice of bread from the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and walk past the kitchen sink, back to the small black shelf on your right side.
Place the bread on the small black shelf, between the head of lettuce closest to the edge of the shelf and the knife you previously used.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled, slice of bread on the shelf by the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn left, move to in front of the low work table.
Pick up the knife that is near the edge.
Turn right, move to the table.
Slice the bread with the knife.
Turn right, move to in front of the low work table.
Put the knife on the low work table.
Turn right, move to the table.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the bred slice in the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the end of the counter, move to in front of the low work table.
Put the bread slice on the low work table.
